#, fuzzy
msgid "but we haven't set them up yet."
msgstr "但我们还没设置好。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Let's see how you can do it with Hibernate Search."
msgstr "让我们来看看如何使用 Hibernate Search 来实现这一点。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Setting up the analyzers"
msgstr "分析仪的设置"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"It is an easy task, we just need to create an implementation of `ElasticsearchAnalysisConfigurer`\n"
"(and configure Quarkus to use it, more on that later)."
msgstr "这是一项简单的任务，我们只需实现 `ElasticsearchAnalysisConfigurer` 接口（并配置 Quarkus 使其使用该实现，相关内容稍后详述）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To fulfill our requirements, let's create the following implementation:"
msgstr "为了满足我们的需求，让我们编写以下实现代码："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Annotate the configurer implementation with the `@SearchExtension` qualifier\n"
"to tell Quarkus it should be used in the default persistence unit, for all Elasticsearch indexes (by default)."
msgstr "在配置器实现中添加 `@SearchExtension` 修饰符，以告知 Quarkus 应将其用于默认持久化单元，并适用于所有 Elasticsearch 索引（默认情况下）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The annotation can also target a specific persistence unit (`@SearchExtension(persistenceUnit = \"nameOfYourPU\")`),\n"
"backend (`@SearchExtension(backend = \"nameOfYourBackend\")`), index (`@SearchExtension(index = \"nameOfYourIndex\")`),\n"
"or a combination of those\n"
"(`@SearchExtension(persistenceUnit = \"nameOfYourPU\", backend = \"nameOfYourBackend\", index = \"nameOfYourIndex\")`)."
msgstr "该注解还可以针对特定的持久化单元 ( `@SearchExtension(persistenceUnit = \"nameOfYourPU\")` )、后端 ( `@SearchExtension(backend = \"nameOfYourBackend\")` )、索引 ( `@SearchExtension(index = \"nameOfYourIndex\")` )，或上述要素的组合 ( `@SearchExtension(persistenceUnit = \"nameOfYourPU\", backend = \"nameOfYourBackend\", index = \"nameOfYourIndex\"))` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is a simple analyzer separating the words on spaces, removing any non-ASCII characters by its ASCII counterpart (and thus removing accents) and putting everything in lowercase.\n"
"It is used in our examples for the author's names."
msgstr "这是一个简单的分析器，它根据空格将单词分隔开来，将所有非ASCII字符替换为相应的ASCII字符（从而去除重音符号），并将所有内容转换为小写。在我们的示例中，它用于处理作者姓名。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We are a bit more aggressive with this one and we include some stemming: we will be able to search for `mystery` and get a result even if the indexed input contains `mysteries`.\n"
"It is definitely too aggressive for person names, but it is perfect for the book titles."
msgstr "对于这一项，我们的处理方式稍微激进一些，并加入了词干提取：这样即使索引中的输入包含 `“mysteries”一词` ，我们也能搜索 `“mystery”` 并获得结果。这种方法对于人名来说显然过于激进，但对于书名来说却再合适不过了。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here is the normalizer used for sorting. Very similar to our first analyzer, except we don't tokenize the words as we want one and only one token."
msgstr "这是用于排序的规范化器。它与我们的第一个分析器非常相似，只是我们不进行词分词，因为我们希望得到且仅得到一个令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Alternatively, if for some reason you can't or don't want to annotate your analysis configurer with `@SearchExtension`,\n"
"you can simply annotate it with `@Dependent @Named(\"myAnalysisConfigurer\")`\n"
"and then reference it from configuration properties:"
msgstr "此外，如果出于某种原因无法或不愿在分析配置器上添加 `@SearchExtension` 注解，只需为其添加 `@Dependent @Named(\"myAnalysisConfigurer\")` 注解，然后在配置属性中引用它即可："

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Adding full text capabilities to our REST service"
msgstr "为我们的 REST 服务添加全文搜索功能"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In our existing `LibraryResource`, we just need to inject the `SearchSession`:"
msgstr "在现有的 `LibraryResource` 中，我们只需注入 `SearchSession` ："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Inject a Hibernate Search session, which relies on the `EntityManager` under the hood.\n"
