#, fuzzy
msgid "Use the `org.jboss.resteasy.reactive.RestQuery` annotation type to avoid repeating the parameter name."
msgstr "使用 `org.jboss.resteasy.reactive.RestQuery` 注解类型，以避免重复使用参数名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We indicate that we are searching for ``Author``s."
msgstr "我们在此说明，我们正在寻找 `作者` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We create a predicate: if the pattern is empty, we use a `matchAll()` predicate."
msgstr "我们定义一个谓词：如果模式为空，则使用 `matchAll()` 谓词。"

#. type: Plain text
