msgstr "运行它就像执行 `./target/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch-quickstart-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-runner` ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can then point your browser to `http://localhost:8080/` and use your application."
msgstr "然后，您可以将浏览器指向 `http://localhost:8080/` 并使用您的应用程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The startup is a bit slower than usual: it is mostly due to us dropping and recreating the database schema and the Elasticsearch mapping every time at startup.\n"
"We also inject some data and execute the mass indexer."
msgstr "启动速度比平时稍慢一些：这主要是因为我们在每次启动时都会删除并重新创建数据库模式和 Elasticsearch 映射。此外，我们还会注入一些数据并运行批量索引程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In a real life application, it is obviously something you won't do at startup."
msgstr "在实际应用中，启动时显然不会这样做。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Offline startup"
msgstr "离线启动"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default, Hibernate Search sends a few requests to the Elasticsearch cluster on startup.\n"
"If the Elasticsearch cluster is not necessarily up and running when Hibernate Search starts,\n"
"this could cause a startup failure."
msgstr "默认情况下，Hibernate Search 在启动时会向 Elasticsearch 集群发送若干请求。如果 Hibernate Search 启动时 Elasticsearch 集群尚未运行，可能会导致启动失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To address this, you can configure Hibernate Search to not send any request on startup:"
msgstr "为了解决这个问题，您可以配置 Hibernate Search，使其在启动时不发送任何请求："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Disable Elasticsearch version checks on startup by setting the configuration property\n"
"link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.elasticsearch.version-check.enabled[`quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.elasticsearch.version-check.enabled`]\n"
"to `false`."
msgstr "将配置属性设置为 link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.elasticsearch.version-check.enabled[quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.elasticsearch.version-check.enabled] 为 `false` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Disable schema management on startup by setting the configuration property\n"
"link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.schema-management.strategy[`quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.schema-management.strategy`]\n"
"to `none`."
msgstr "将配置属性设置为 link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.schema-management.strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.schema-management.strategy] 设置为 `none` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Of course, even with this configuration, Hibernate Search still won't be able to index anything or run search queries\n"
"until the Elasticsearch cluster becomes accessible."
msgstr "当然，即使采用这种配置，在 Elasticsearch 集群可访问之前，Hibernate Search 仍然无法进行索引或执行搜索查询。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you disable automatic schema creation by setting `quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.schema-management.strategy` to `none`,\n"
"you will have to create the schema manually at some point before your application starts persisting/updating entities\n"
"and executing search requests."
msgstr "如果您通过将 `quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.schema-management.strategy` 设置为 `none` 来禁用自动模式创建功能，那么在应用程序开始持久化/更新实体以及执行搜索请求之前，您必须在某个时间点手动创建该模式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"See link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#mapper-orm-schema-management-manager[this section of the reference documentation]\n"
"for more information."
msgstr "更多信息，请参阅 link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#mapper-orm-schema-management-manager[参考文档的这一部分] 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Coordination through outbox polling"
msgstr "通过“发件箱”轮询实现协调"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Coordination through outbox polling is considered preview."
msgstr "通过“发件箱轮询”进行的协调目前仍处于预览阶段。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In _preview_, backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed.\n"
"Specific improvements might require changing configuration or APIs, or even storage formats,\n"
"and plans to become _stable_ are under way.\n"
"Feedback is welcome on our https://groups.google.com/d/forum/quarkus-dev[mailing list]\n"
"or as issues in our https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[GitHub issue tracker]."
msgstr "在 _预览版中_ ，无法保证向后兼容性及在生态系统中的可用性。某些具体改进可能需要更改配置、API，甚至存储格式， _相关稳定版_ 开发计划正在推进中。欢迎通过我们的 link:https://groups.google.com/d/forum/quarkus-dev[邮件列表] 或在我们 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues[GitHub 问题跟踪器] 中提交问题来提供反馈。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While it’s technically possible to use Hibernate Search and Elasticsearch in distributed applications,\n"
"by default they suffer from\n"
"link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#architecture-examples-no-coordination-elasticsearch-pros-and-cons[a few limitations]."
msgstr "虽然在分布式应用程序中使用 Hibernate Search 和 Elasticsearch 在技术上是可行的，但默认情况下它们会受到 link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#architecture-examples-no-coordination-elasticsearch-pros-and-cons[一些限制] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "These limitations are the result of Hibernate Search not coordinating between threads or application nodes by default."
msgstr "这些限制是由于 Hibernate Search 默认情况下不会在线程或应用程序节点之间进行协调所致。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In order to get rid of these limitations, you can\n"
"link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#architecture-examples-outbox-polling-elasticsearch[use the `outbox-polling` coordination strategy].\n"
"This strategy creates an outbox table in the database to push entity change events to,\n"
"and relies on a background processor to consume these events and perform automatic indexing."
msgstr "为了摆脱这些限制，可以 link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#architecture-examples-outbox-polling-elasticsearch[使用outbox-polling 协调策略] 。该策略会在数据库中创建一个发件箱表，将实体变更事件推送到该表中，并依靠后台处理器来处理这些事件和执行自动索引。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To enable the `outbox-polling` coordination strategy, an additional extension is required:"
msgstr "要启用 `“发件箱轮询”` 协调策略，需要一个额外的扩展："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Once the extension is there, you will need to explicitly select the `outbox-polling` strategy\n"
"by setting link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.coordination.strategy[`quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.coordination.strategy`]\n"
"to `outbox-polling`."
msgstr "一旦扩展到位，您需要明确选择 `outbox-polling` 策略，将其设置为 link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.coordination.strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.coordination.strategy] 为 `outbox-polling` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Finally, you will need to make sure that the Hibernate ORM entities added by Hibernate Search\n"
"(to represent the outbox and agents) have corresponding tables/sequences in your database:"
msgstr "最后，您需要确保由 Hibernate Search 添加的 Hibernate ORM 实体（用于表示“发件箱”和“代理”）在您的数据库中拥有相应的表/序列："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you are just starting with your application\n"
"and intend to xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#dev-mode[let Hibernate ORM generate your database schema],\n"
"then no worries: the entities required by Hibernate Search will be included in the generated schema."
msgstr "如果您刚刚开始开发应用程序，并且打算 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#dev-mode[让 Hibernate ORM 生成数据库模式] ，那么请放心：Hibernate Search 所需的实体将会包含在生成的模式中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Otherwise, you must\n"
"link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#coordination-outbox-polling-schema[manually alter your schema to add the necessary tables/sequences]."
msgstr "否则，您必须 link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#coordination-outbox-polling-schema[手动更改模式以添加必要的表/序列] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Once you are done with the above, you're ready to use Hibernate Search with an outbox.\n"
"Don't change any code, and just start your application:\n"
"it will automatically detect when multiple applications are connected to the same database,\n"
"and coordinate the index updates accordingly."
msgstr "完成上述操作后，您就可以在“发件箱”中使用 Hibernate Search 了。无需修改任何代码，只需启动应用程序即可：当多个应用程序连接到同一数据库时，系统会自动检测到这一情况，并据此协调索引更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hibernate Search mostly behaves the same when using the `outbox-polling` coordination strategy\n"
"as when not using it: application code (persisting entities, searching, etc.) should not require any change."
msgstr "在使用 `“出站箱轮询”` 协调策略时，Hibernate Search 的行为与不使用该策略时基本一致：应用程序代码（持久化实体、搜索等）无需进行任何修改。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"However, there is one key difference: index updates are necessarily asynchronous;\n"
"they are guaranteed to happen _eventually_, but not immediately."
msgstr "不过，两者有一个关键区别：索引更新必然是异步的；虽然保证 _最终_ 会发生，但不会立即发生。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This means in particular that the configuration property\n"
"link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.automatic-indexing.synchronization.strategy[`quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.automatic-indexing.synchronization.strategy`]\n"
"cannot be set when using the `outbox-polling` coordination strategy:\n"
"Hibernate Search will always behave as if this property was set to `write-sync` (the default)."
msgstr "这尤其意味着 link:#quarkus-hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch_quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.automatic-indexing.synchronization.strategy[quarkus.hibernate-search-orm.automatic-indexing.synchronization.strategy] 在使用 `outbox-polling` 协调策略时无法设置：Hibernate Search 将始终按照将此属性设置为 `write-sync` （默认值）的方式运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This behavior is consistent with Elasticsearch's\n"
"https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/near-real-time.html[near-real-time search]\n"
"and the recommended way of using Hibernate Search even when coordination is disabled."
msgstr "这种行为符合 Elasticsearch 的 link:https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/near-real-time.html[近实时搜索特性] ，也是即使在禁用协调功能时使用 Hibernate Search 的推荐方式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For more information about coordination in Hibernate Search,\n"
"see link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#coordination[this section of the reference documentation]."
msgstr "有关 Hibernate Search 中协调的更多信息，请参阅 link:{hibernate-search-doc-prefix}#coordination[参考文档的这一部分] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For more information about configuration options related to coordination,\n"
"see <<configuration-reference-coordination-outbox-polling>>."
msgstr "有关协调相关配置选项的更多信息，请参阅 <<configuration-reference-coordination-outbox-polling>> 。"

#. type: Title =
#: _versions/2.16/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "[[configuration-reference-aws]] AWS request signing"
msgstr "AWS 请求签名"

#. type: Plain text
